msgid "<app>Orca</app> works with applications and toolkits that support the Assistive Technology Service Provider Interface (AT-SPI), which is the primary assistive technology infrastructure for Linux and Solaris. Applications and toolkits supporting the AT-SPI include Gtk+, Qt, Java Swing, LibreOffice, Gecko, WebKitGtk, and Chrome/Chromium."
